# Preon Brand (template)

When creating or editing branded UI/copy for Preon, follow the official design system:

- Repo: https://github.com/preon-solutions/preon-brand-identity
- Visual system: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/preon-solutions/preon-brand-identity/main/visual-system.md
- Voice: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/preon-solutions/preon-brand-identity/main/voice.md

Defaults: cream background `#F7F4EF`, text `#1C1917`, primary `#7C6FAF`, Source Serif 4 headlines, IBM Plex Mono body/UI.

Use official logo URLs from the repo. Avoid pure black backgrounds, glassmorphism, candy gradients, and startup-flash aesthetics.

For full workflow and asset URLs, use the `preon-brand` skill in the brand-identity repo.
